Use the standard library
This is how to sort_even of l:
   Remember that evens is []
   Remember that i is 0

   Do this l's length times:
      When remainder of item i in l and 2 is 0, then:
         Add evens to item i in l
      End when
      Increase i
   End do

   Remember that n is evens's length
   Do this n times:
      Remember that j is 0
      Do this n times:
         When j is less than diff of n and 1, then:
            When item j in evens is more than item (sum of j and 1) in evens, then:
               Remember that temp is item j in evens
               Remember that item j in evens is item (sum of j and 1) in evens
               Remember that item (sum of j and 1) in evens is temp
            End when
         End when
         Increase j
      End do
   End do

   Remember that result is []
   Remember that i is 0
   Remember that e is 0

   Do this l's length times:
      When remainder of item i in l and 2 is 0, then:
         Add result to item e in evens
         Increase e
      But, if not:
         Add result to item i in l
      End when
      Increase i
   End do

   The answer is result
